snippet.title: Stop Dead - Official Announcement Trailer | gamescom 2023
snippet.description:
Stop Dead will be available on Steam and the Epic Games Store on October 5, 2023. Watch the action-packed trailer to see more from this upcoming first-person telekinetic brawler game.

In Stop Dead, don’t stop moving across a chaotic, comic book-inspired cityscape where catching a breath brings instant death. Stop Dead features 40 levels, four biomes, and you can use superhuman abilities to pick up over 160 unique throwable objects like guns, chainsaws and the bloodied, still-warm corpses of recent slaughter (hooray!).
